                                    Path = network/PacketFlowGenerator.h
                                    Description = Generates packets using 2 distributions read from parameters: 1) for the packetSize 2) for the interleave time between each packet generation\n inPort0: can receive events that force the generation of a new packet the moment of the event arrival (can be used to generate packets following an outside source distribution)\n outPort0: generated packets
